Date: 0/0/1989
Source: NZ English Newsletter
Author:
Vol / Page: 3/28
Edition:
Quote: <i>sheep-oh</i>: The call of the shearer when he wants the penner-up to refill his catching pen. This call cannot be made while there are more than two sheep left in the pen.
Notes: Wallace Shearing

